&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1:04:30 Why gender-based discussions suck so bad.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hoping we can get through this topic with minimal loss of life.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Often people tone down their criticism when talking about indie games. I know I do.  It’s easy to dump on a huge multi-million dollar project with hundreds of contributors. But when you’re talking about something made by half a dozen people, it all becomes kind of personal and I’m shy of eviscerating something on that level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But sometimes you have to give a game the thrashing it deserves. This week is a reckoning for a handful of misbegotten indies.&lt;/p&gt;
